Name: Too Fast, Too Furious
Description: Completed performance faster than the ideal time.

Name: Slow and Steady
Description: Completed performance faster than the standard time.

Name: 10 Ways to Die
Description: Used between two and ten unique spell types.

Name: 4 Ways to Die
Description: Used two, three, or four unique spell types.

Name: Can't Touch This
Description: Took zero damage.

Name: Ain't Got Time to Bleed
Description: Restored zero HP.

Name: Modus Interruptus
Description: Interrupted a target's casting.

Name: A Walk in the Park
Description: Refrained from using Sprint.

Name: Mastery of Fire
Description: Used one or more fire-aspected spells. Spells aspected to other elements were not used.

Name: Mastery of Water
Description: Used one or more water-aspected spells. Spells aspected to other elements were not used.

Name: Mastery of Earth
Description: Used one or more earth-aspected spells. Spells aspected to other elements were not used.

Name: Mastery of Wind
Description: Used one or more wind-aspected spells. Spells aspected to other elements were not used.

Name: Mastery of Ice
Description: Used one or more ice-aspected spells. Spells aspected to other elements were not used.

Name: Mastery of Lightning
Description: Used one or more lightning-aspected spells. Spells aspected to other elements were not used.

Name: Elemental Mastery
Description: Cast spells aspected to all six elements.

Name: Total Mastery
Description: Used actions aspected to all six elements and three damage types (blunt, piercing, slashing).

Name: Enfeeble Me Tender
Description: Applied six or more unique enfeeblements.

Name: Enfeeble Me Tenderer
Description: Applied nine or more unique enfeeblements.

Name: Let's Get Physical
Description: Used only physical-type actions.

Name: Advanced Spellcasting
Description: Cast only rank 4 or 5 spells.

Name: Beginner Spellcasting
Description: Cast only rank 1 or 2 spells.

Name: Four-faced
Description: Used four or more unique actions that are fired from the face.

Name: Eight-faced
Description: Used eight or more unique actions that are fired from the face.

Name: Hooked on a Healing
Description: Use Pom Cure, Exuviation, and White Wind.
